dal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ywi1665702822380_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywi1665702822380_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywi1665702822380_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ywi1665702822380\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Delete ...\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether Uniface deletes spaces, zeros, or control characters before the characters entered in the field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__section_w2864ab1b5b1_w2865ab1b5_w2866ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Data Clean-Up Options</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\"> Field </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\"> Action </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Leading Spaces</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete spaces before the first non-space\n                        character. (True = <code class=\"ph codeph\">DLS</code>, False = <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDLS</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Leading Zeros</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete zeros before the first nonzero\n                        character. (True = <code class=\"ph codeph\">DLZ</code>, False = <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDLZ</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Leading Control</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete non-printing control characters before\n                        the first non-control character in the data, except for carriage returns,\n                        form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs. (True =\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">DLC</code>, False = <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDLC</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Control</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete carriage returns, form feeds, line\n                        feeds, tabs and vertical tabs, wherever they are in the data. (True =\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">YDCC</code>, False = <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDCC</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Text Control</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete non-printing control characters except\n                        for carriage returns, form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs,\n                        wherever they are in the data. (True = <code class=\"ph codeph\">YDCX</code>, False =\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDCX</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Trailing Control</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ywi1665702822380__table_d11474e1_d11475e1_d11476e1__entry__2\">Delete non-printing control characters after\n                        the last non-control character in the data, except for carriage returns,\n                        form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs. (True =\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">DTC</code>, False = <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDTC</code>) </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__section_q5j_frq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1107010e191\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywi1665702822380__p_d99089e1_d99090e1_d99091e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424344\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424344\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Delete ... Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete ... Specify whether Uniface deletes spaces, zeros, or control characters before the characters entered in the field. Table 1. Data Clean-Up Options Field Action Leading Spaces Delete spaces before the first non-space character. (True = DLS , False = NDLS ) Leading Zeros Delete zeros before the first nonzero character. (True = DLZ , False = NDLZ ) Leading Control Delete non-printing control characters before the first non-control character in the data, except for carriage returns, form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs. (True = DLC , False = NDLC ) Control Delete carriage returns, form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs, wherever they are in the data. (True = YDCC , False = NDCC ) Text Control Delete non-printing control characters except for carriage returns, form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs, wherever they are in the data. (True = YDCX , False = NDCX ) Trailing Control Delete non-printing control characters after the last non-control character in the data, except for carriage returns, form feeds, line feeds, tabs and vertical tabs. (True = DTC , False = NDTC ) Applies To Field Syntax Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}